<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 13 at 6:58AM EST  by NWS Detroit</headline>
<description>...Some Black Ice This Morning...
Moisture deposited on the roads last night is now turning to ice
as temperatures drop below freezing. This has created some black
ice on area roads. Drivers should use caution this morning as this
type of ice can be difficult to see on the roads. The slick
conditions are likely to persist well into the morning as
temperatures hold below freezing.</description>
